<partial name="~/Views/Shared/Partials/_NavbarUser.cshtml" />

<div class="container">
    <h1 class="text-center my-5">Chat Messages</h1>

    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8">
            <div class="media">
                <img class="mr-3 rounded-circle" src="https://via.placeholder.com/64x64" alt="User Avatar">
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">John Doe</h5>
                    <p>Hey, how are you doing?</p>
                    <p>Did you hear about the new update?</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="media">
                <img class="mr-3 rounded-circle" src="https://via.placeholder.com/64x64" alt="User Avatar">
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">Jane Smith</h5>
                    <p>Yeah, I saw the announcement earlier today. It looks pretty interesting.</p>
                    <p>What do you think?</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="media">
                <img class="mr-3 rounded-circle" src="https://via.placeholder.com/64x64" alt="User Avatar">
                <div class="media-body">
                    <h5 class="mt-0">John Doe</h5>
                    <p>I think it's going to be a game-changer for sure.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <form>
        <div class="form-group row">
            <label for="inputMessage" class="col-sm-2 col-form-label">Message</label>
            <div class="col-sm-8">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" id="inputMessage" placeholder="Type your message here...">
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2">
                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Send</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>